name: Trying to find myself
description: I try to describe myself. Actually I have nothing. I can't do anything. I am not good enough. Everything is a gift. All things in my life runs by the Creator of the universe. But even though it was very difficult, I tried to look within myself to find my true Creator. It's so complicated to think about this, because the brain can burst and it won't get to thinking about this. Must be silent and empty or turn off this self.
